Nielsen Study: Responding to criticisms from the television networks over the 
recent case of "disappearing viewers," the A. C. Nielsen Co. has agreed to 
study the possibility of combining its current "people-meter" ratings system 
with some other kinds of audience measurement. The networks have contended that 
flaws in the "people-meter" system are responsible for the recent drop in TV 
viewing shown in the Nielsen ratings. See "By the Numbers" below for a look at 
